    {
      "id": "detailed_3_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This vehicle is in good, dependable condition and has been well-maintained over the years. The exterior is in great shape overall but does show minor signs of regular use, such as a few small stone chips on the hood and light surface scratches. Inside, the cabin is clean and comfortable, with all major features and electronics functioning as expected. Mechanically, the car is solid and ready for the road, offering a smooth and reliable driving experience for its next owner.",
