    {
      "id": "sybil_0_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "Presenting an unrivaled example of automotive excellence. This vehicle is offered in impeccable, showroom condition, representing the pinnacle of its class. Meticulously maintained and showing virtually no signs of wear, it provides a rare opportunity for the discerning collector or enthusiast who demands nothing less than perfection. This is an investment-grade specimen that must be seen to be fully appreciated.",
