    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "This vehicle is a true time capsule, preserved in showroom condition since day one. The exterior boasts a deep, mirror-like finish with absolutely zero chips, dings, or swirls, having been professionally ceramic coated and strictly garage-kept. Inside, the cabin remains pristine; the premium leather seats show no signs of wear, the original floor mats are spotless, and that signature 'new car' scent still lingers. Every button, switch, and technological feature functions exactly as it did the day it rolled off the assembly line. Mechanically, it is flawless, backed by a comprehensive, documented service history performed exclusively at the dealership. With exceptionally low mileage and a smooth, responsive drive, this car represents the pinnacle of its model year. It\u2019s not just a used car; it\u2019s a collector-grade example ready for its next owner who demands perfection.",
      "price": 44900.0,
      "reputation": 0.5,
